								Dear Energy  Professional,
								
								Please accept this invitation  to take a free look at 888  Annotated, the 
only authoritative guide to FERC's Open Access  Transmission Tariff (OATT). 
888 Annotated  reports the full, relevant text of all FERC rulings which 
interpret OATTs  adopted by the nation's jurisdictional and 
non-jurisdictional electric  utilities.
								
								We have just opened a website  on which we have posted a beta version of our 
most recent edition of 888  Annotated. Pending final publication in June, we 
invite you to make as  much use of this beta version of 888 Annotated as you 
like without charge.  Just click here to visit us. And please give us your 
comments -  particularly about how you think we might improve 888 Annotated  
on the web. 
								
								If this communication or future announcements  pertaining to 888 Annotated  
is not welcome, please let us know by replying to this e-mail, indicating  
the word "unsubscribe" in the subject line. Whether you unsubscribe or  not, 
be assured that we will never share your e-mail address with anyone  else.
								
								Sincerely yours,
								
								Donald R.  Allen
								
								
